message: Hi Bob, I'd like to offer you my product at a price of $200. I believe this price reflects its exceptional quality and value. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding or if you have any thoughts on the pricing.

Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. However, $200 is a bit out of my budget. I'm willing to pay up to $120 for the product, considering its quality and my current financial situation. Let me know what you think!
